      "span_text": "Modeling is a useful exercise, in anticipation of how a S. aureus vaccine would be used, were it to be licensed and deployed.  The authors simulated stochastic susceptible-infected-recovered dynamics on social networks, based on observations in a hospital in Tokyo, in an exploration of different containment strategies directed against nosocomial infections."
